{
  "id": "019d3202-020c-75c3-bc68-4d82cd89d535",
  "content": "## Tiered Knowledge Dashboard Implementation (Issue #25)\n\nImplemented 4 dashboard visualization components for the tiered knowledge lifecycle:\n\n### API Endpoints Added\n- `GET /api/dashboard/tiers` — tier distribution (hot/warm/cold/forgotten counts) + forgetting enabled flag\n- `GET /api/dashboard/tiers/transitions` — recent tier transitions parsed from structured trace logs (tier_transition events)\n- `GET /api/dashboard/tiers/pinned` — pinned entries list via knowledge JSON scan\n- `GET /api/dashboard/tiers/gc-history` — knowledge GC cycle reports from GcKnowledgeHistory ring buffer\n- `POST /api/dashboard/tiers/unpin/{entry_id}` — unpin entry (with frontend confirmation gate)\n\n### Key Design Decisions\n- Tier distribution uses direct LiteStore downcast (`count_tiers_by_scope`) rather than full `system_status` call for performance\n- Tier transitions are parsed from `corvia-traces.log` structured events (message=\"tier_transition\"), read from end for recency\n- File I/O for transition parsing wrapped in `spawn_blocking` to prevent async runtime starvation\n- Content preview truncation uses `char_indices()` for UTF-8 safety (not byte slicing)\n- Frontend uses `window.confirm()` before unpin to match MCP confirmation pattern\n- New \"Tiers\" tab added to dashboard Layout, with 2-column responsive grid\n\n### Frontend Components (Preact/TSX)\n- TierDistributionChart: stacked bar with legend, ARIA labels\n- RecentTransitions: table with tier badges, cross-tab deeplinks via navigateToHistory\n- PinnedEntries: list with unpin button (confirmation + disabled state during request)\n- GcHistoryTimeline: SVG sparkline + latest cycle stats with transition breakdown\n\n### Review Findings Addressed\n- UTF-8 panic on multi-byte content (Critical)\n- Async runtime blocking from sync file read (Important)\n- Missing unpin confirmation and loading state (Important)\n- Silent error swallowing from usePoll (Important)\n- Missing cross-tab entry deeplinks (Important)\n- Empty state guidance text (Important)\n- ARIA accessibility labels (Important)",
  "source_version": "mcp",
  "scope_id": "corvia",
  "workstream": "main",
